"```sql\nSELECT \n    CAST(COUNT(*) AS REAL) * 100 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM superhero s \n     INNER JOIN publisher p ON s.publisher_id = p.id \n     WHERE p.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics') AS percentage\nFROM \n    superhero s \nINNER JOIN \n    alignment a ON s.alignment_id = a.id \nINNER JOIN \n    publisher p ON s.publisher_id = p.id \nWHERE \n    p.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics' AND a.alignment = 'Bad';\n```"